</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Correlating eligibility criteria generalizability and adverse events using Big Data for patients and clinical trials</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sen%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Anando Sen</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Anando Sen</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Columbia University, New York, New York
</div>
